I am building a production-quality machine learning inference engine in C++ from scratch. The goal is to deeply understand and demonstrate high-performance computing, memory optimization, and systems-level design.

This project is NOT a school assignment. It must be structured, clean, benchmarked, and interview-ready.

The system will load pretrained model weights (from Python/PyTorch), run inference in C++, and benchmark performance against Python implementations.

